<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-tanCerca" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Conversación numérica: Tan cerca</title>

<statement>
  <p>Encuentra mentalmente el valor de cada expresión.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <p> <m>9 + 6</m></p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p> <m>29 + 6</m></p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p> <m>59 + 6</m></p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p> <m>49 + 8</m></p>
    </li>
  </ul>
 
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>15: I just know it. I took one away from 6 and added it to the 9 to make 10 and then added the leftover 5, which makes 15.</li>
      <li>35: I took 1 away from 6 and added it to the 29 to make 30 and then added the leftover 5 to make 35.</li>
      <li>65: I changed 59 to 60 and then added 6 to get 66. Then I subtracted 1 to make up for the extra 1, which makes 65.</li>
      <li>57: I took 1 away from the 8 and added it to the 49 to make 50 and then added 50 and 7 to get 57.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


